Module FillTheFormAPI.main

Package pl.edu.pwr.pkuchnowski.filltheformapi

package pl.edu.pwr.pkuchnowski.filltheformapi
This package contains the main class for the FillTheFormAPI application.

The application is built using Spring Boot and Gradle. It includes several components:

  • Controllers to handle incoming requests
  • Services to interact with forms
  • FormGetters (implementations of the FormService interface) to get form links
  • Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) to encapsulate data for network transfer
  • Configuration to set up the application

Each component is represented by a sub-package within this package.
